<i>noun</i>: 호연지기 [호ː연지기], 호기 [호기] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>호연지기 [호ː연지기]</dt><br>
<dd>magnanimousness; gallantry; great spirit</dd><br>
<dd>넓고 큰 마음과 굳은 신념.</dd><br>
<dd>Broad-mindedness and strong conviction.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>호기 [호기]</dt><br>
<dd>1. gallantry; intrepidity</dd><br>
<dd>씩씩하고 큰 기상.</dd><br>
<dd>A gallant and brave spirit.</dd><br>
<dd>2. arrogance; pomposity</dd><br>
<dd>거만한 태도로 잘난 척하는 기운.</dd><br>
<dd>An attitude of putting on airs and behaving arrogantly.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>